## üöÄ About This Project

This Hot Reload system for Revit 2026 C# plugins was created through collaborative development between:

- **Philip K√∂nig** - Revit expertise, real-world testing, and architectural guidance
- **Claude (Anthropic)** - Code implementation, documentation, and technical architecture

The project represents a breakthrough in Revit plugin development, enabling 6x faster development cycles through genuine Hot Reload functionality without Revit restarts.

